<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-bs-theme="auto">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Register</title>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<main class="container" style="max-width: 640px;">
    <h1 class="mb-1">Create an Account</h1>
    <p class="text-body-secondary mb-4">
        Join <strong>altx10.dev</strong> to access a set of free, user-focused, open-source applications.
    </p>
    <p>
        Accounts are managed through a hosted <strong>Pocket ID</strong> instance
        <a href="https://account.altx10.dev">account.altx10.dev</a>.
        Only passkeys are used for authentication &mdash; no passwords are
        stored. Only minimal information is required to register, and your info will never be used for advertising
        or shared with third parties. We do not intentionally track any personal information beyond what is required to
        use one of our particular applications.
    </p>
    <div class="card mb-4">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-title fw-bold mb-3">Before registering, please review and accept the following:</p>
            <ul class="mb-0">
                <li>You assert that you are <strong>13 years of age or older</strong>.</li>
                <li>Your information is not used for marketing, sales, or shared with any third parties.</li>
                <li>This software is provided as-is, with no support and no guarantees of continued operation.</li>
                <li>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts at any time, for any reason, without notice.
                </li>
                <li>We are not liable for any data loss, damages, or issues arising from your use of these services.
                </li>
                <li>These terms may be updated at any time. Continued use of the service constitutes acceptance of any
                    changes.
                </li>
                <li>You agree not to use these services for any unlawful or abusive purpose.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <form method="POST" action="/register">
        <input type="hidden" name="csrfToken" value="{{csrfToken}}">
        <div class="form-check mb-3">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="consent" value="true" id="consent" required>
            <label class="form-check-label" for="consent">
                I have read and agree to the above terms.
            </label>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100">Register</button>
    </form>
    <p class="text-body-secondary text-center small mt-3">
        You will be redirected to <a href="https://account.altx10.dev">account.altx10.dev</a> to complete registration.
    </p>
    <p class="text-center mt-2"><a href="/login">Already have an account? Login</a></p>
</main>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script>
    (function () {
        const theme = window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches ? 'dark' : 'light';
        document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-bs-theme', theme);
        window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').addEventListener('change', function (e) {
            document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-bs-theme', e.matches ? 'dark' : 'light');
        });
    })();
</script>

</body>
</html>
